## SpaceModels API

### Account Operations
- `crud_account.create(db, obj_in={})` - Create new account
- `crud_account.get_by_email(db, email="")` - Get account by email
- `crud_account.get_by_username(db, username="")` - Get account by username
- `crud_account.create_with_organization(db, obj_in={}, organization_id="", role="owner")` - Create account linked to organization
- `crud_account.get_active(db, skip=0, limit=100)` - Get active accounts
- `crud_account.deactivate(db, id="")` - Deactivate account

### Tracker Operations
- `crud_tracker.create(db, obj_in={})` - Create new tracker
- `crud_tracker.validate_connection(db, tracker_id="")` - Validate tracker connection and update status
- `crud_tracker.get_for_account(db, account_id="", tracker_type=None)` - Get trackers for account
- `crud_tracker.get_active(db, skip=0, limit=100)` - Get active trackers
- `crud_tracker.deactivate(db, id="")` - Deactivate tracker

